    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>fries</strong> to the baking tray with <strong>half</strong> the <strong>ground smoked paprika</strong> (you'll use the rest later!), a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> and a small pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>hot dog</strong> <strong>sausages</strong> to the other side of the baking tray</p><p>Tip: Cooking for 4? Use 2 trays!</p><p>Put the tray<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span> in the oven for 20-25 min or until the sausages are cooked through – these are your <strong>sausages and smoky fries</strong></p>",
