    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine the <strong>carrot & cabbage slaw mix</strong> with <strong>half</strong> the <strong>mayo </strong>(you'll use the rest later!), the <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>white wine vinegar </strong>and a small pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper </strong>–<strong> </strong>this is your<strong> slaw</strong></p><p>Combine the<strong> remaining mayo </strong>and the<strong> mustard ketchup </strong>in a small bowl with a small splash of<strong> cold water</strong> – this is your<strong> mustard-mayo dip</strong></p>",
