    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the sausages are cooked through, remove the tray<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span> from the oven and transfer them to a clean chopping board to cool slightly</p><p>Cut a slit into the top of each<strong> hot dog bun </strong>and add them to the tray</p><p>Return the tray to the oven for 2-3 min or until the buns are warmed through and the fries are golden</p>",
