    {
      "instruction": "<p>Slice the <strong>cooled sausages</strong> on the diagonal, into bite-sized pieces</p><p>Add the <strong>sliced sausages </strong>to the pan of curry ketchup and give everything a good mix up until well coated</p><p>Return the pan to a low heat and cook for 30 secs to reheat – these are your<strong> currywurst-style sausages</strong></p>",
