      "instruction": "<p>Fill each<strong> hot dog bun </strong>with the <strong>currywurst-style sausages</strong>, then top with the <strong>caramelised onion</strong></p><p>Sprinkle over the <strong>reserved curry powder</strong></p><p>Serve the <strong>smoky fries</strong>,<strong> slaw</strong> and <strong>mustard-mayo dip </strong>to the side</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
